                //- a(href='/', style='color:#fff')
                button.btn.mt-5.btn-outline-light.btn-custom.btn-block.text-uppercase.rounded-pill.btn-lg(type='submit')
                    | Login
                p.mt-3.font-weight-normal
                    | Don't have an account! 
                    a(href='/registration', style='color:#666;text-decoration: underline;')
                        strong  REGISTER NOW!
